763
00:27:10,000 --> 00:27:11,000
 Ja nema, ja ću doma ostati,

764
00:27:11,000 --> 00:27:12,000
 moram naravnoći za faks.

765
00:27:12,000 --> 00:27:14,000
 Ja sam ti učio ravno sati po vremena,

766
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:16,000
