769
00:27:19,000 --> 00:27:21,000
 Znači, to je bilo ono time of my life,

770
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:22,000
 znači, ono, taj hajgo,

771
00:27:22,000 --> 00:27:23,000
 jedno, 15 traka,

772
00:27:23,000 --> 00:27:25,000
 ne znači li duži i širi,

773
00:27:25,000 --> 00:27:26,000
