00:27:41,000 --> 00:27:42,000
 skrenuo slučajno bio.

786
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:45,000
 I onda vraćao se na rutu nekako,

787
00:27:45,000 --> 00:27:46,000
 ne znam pojima,

788
00:27:46,000 --> 00:27:47,000
 znači, katastrofa.

789
00:27:47,000 --> 00:27:48,000
