00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:48,000
 i pita mi koliko ima Kronica

903
00:30:48,000 --> 00:30:49,000
 od Splita do Zagreba.

904
00:30:49,000 --> 00:30:51,000
 Šta ravno tri ružarija.

